data.comment: The first-half is just kicking off.
Cadiz are pushing forward but Jose Mari's finish is wide of the goal.
In the minute 1, It's a goal kick for the away team in Cadiz.
Osasuna awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Cadiz in their own half.

Cadiz awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Osasuna in their own half.
In the minute 6, Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards the home team a throw-in.
Osasuna awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in for Osasuna in their own half.
In the minute 10, Osasuna take a 0-1 lead thanks to Adrian Lopez.
Oier with an assist there.
Corner awarded to Osasuna.

Ball safe as Osasuna is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Throw-in Osasuna.

Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Osasuna in their own half.

Osasuna have a goal kick.

Throw-in for Osasuna in their own half.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards Cadiz a goal kick.

Throw-in Cadiz.

Jon Moncayola for Osasuna gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Ball goes out of play for a Cadiz goal kick.
In the minute 28, Ball safe as Osasuna is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards the away team a throw-in.
Cadiz awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 30, Can Osasuna get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Cadiz's half?
Osasuna have a dangerous throw-in.
Cadiz awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 35, Free kick for Cadiz in the half of Osasuna.
David Garcia for Osasuna has been booked by Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos and receives a first yellow card.
Throw-in for Osasuna at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
In the minute 36, Throw-in for Cadiz in their own half.
Throw-in for Cadiz in the half of Osasuna.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 39, Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards the away team a throw-in.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a Cadiz throw-in in Osasuna's half.
In Cadiz a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 41, Yann Bodiger of Cadiz is pulled up for offside.
Throw-in for Osasuna in the half of Cadiz.
Cadiz have a goal kick.
In the minute 44, Osasuna awarded a free kick in their own half.
Corner awarded to Cadiz.
Sergio (Cadiz) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
In the minute 45, It's a goal kick for the away team in Cadiz.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos will wait an extra 3 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 1st half.
Throw-in for Osasuna at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
In the minute 45, Throw-in Cadiz.
The first-half has come to a close in Cadiz.
The second-half is underway in Cadiz.
In the minute 46, Alvaro Cervera is making the team's first substitution at Estadio Ramon de Carranza with Filip Malbasic replacing Yann Bodiger.
Ball goes out of play for a Cadiz goal kick.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Cadiz in their own half.
In the minute 48, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Cadiz have been awarded a corner by Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos.
Throw-in high up the field for Osasuna in Cadiz.
In the minute 50, Free kick for Cadiz in their own half.
Cadiz needs to be cautious. Osasuna have an attacking throw-in.
Free kick Osasuna.
In the minute 51, Cadiz awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Osasuna.
David Garcia (Osasuna) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 54, Cadiz have been awarded a corner by Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards Osasuna a goal kick.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Osasuna.
In the minute 56, Osasuna's Roberto Torres breaks free at Estadio Ramon de Carranza. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Goal kick for Cadiz at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
Cadiz to take a throw-in in Osasuna territory.
In the minute 58, Free kick for Osasuna in their own half.

Osasuna have a goal kick.
In the minute 61, Ball goes out of play for a Cadiz goal kick.
Free kick for Cadiz in the half of Osasuna.

In the minute 64, Corner awarded to Cadiz.
Throw-in for Osasuna in their own half.
Alex is on a sub for Jose Mari for Cadiz.
In the minute 64, Alvaro Cervera (Cadiz) is making a second substitution, with Jens Jonsson replacing Marcos Mauro.
Free kick Cadiz.
Juan Cruz (Osasuna) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 65, Salvi Sanchez is writhing in pain and play has been suspended for a few moments.
Corner awarded to Cadiz.
Ball safe as Osasuna is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 68, Cadiz are whistled for offside.
Salvi Sanchez is back on his feet again.
Throw-in for Osasuna at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
In the minute 69, Can Cadiz get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Osasuna's half?
Free kick for Osasuna in the half of Cadiz.
Free kick Osasuna.
In the minute 71, The away team replace Inigo Perez with Lucas Torro.
Cadiz pushes forward through Salvi Sanchez, whose finish on goal is saved.
Jorge Pombo of Cadiz smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
In the minute 73, Cadiz have been awarded a corner by Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos.
Osasuna awarded a free kick in their own half.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Cadiz.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards the away team a throw-in.

Ivan Alejo (Cadiz) has replaced the possibly injured Salvi Sanchez.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Cadiz in their own half.
In the minute 78, Anthony Lozano is replacing Alvaro Negredo for Cadiz at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a Cadiz throw-in in Osasuna's half.
Throw-in for Osasuna close to the penalty box.
It's now 0-2 in Cadiz as Ruben Garcia scores for Osasuna.
In the minute 79, Lucas Torro instrumental with a fine assist.
In the minute 82, Osasuna awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Cadiz awarded a free kick in their own half.
Osasuna will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Cadiz.
In the minute 84, Cadiz attack but Jens Jonsson's header doesn't find the target.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards Osasuna a goal kick.
Osasuna make their third substitution with Enrique Barja replacing Ruben Garcia.
In the minute 86, Goal kick for Cadiz at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
Throw-in Osasuna.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos signals a free kick to Osasuna.
In the minute 88, Throw-in for Cadiz in the half of Osasuna.
Free kick for Cadiz in their own half.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos awards the away team a throw-in.
In Cadiz a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Cadiz have a goal kick.
5 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
Goal kick for Osasuna at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
Throw-in for Cadiz at Estadio Ramon de Carranza.
Ball goes out of play for a Osasuna goal kick.
At Estadio Ramon de Carranza, Osasuna are penalized for being offside.
Cadiz awarded a free kick in their own half.
In Cadiz Cadiz attack through Juan Cala. The finish is off target, however.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Cadiz.
Free kick Cadiz.
Isidro Diaz de Mera Escuderos blows to end the match. The final score is 0-2.
At Estadio Ramon de Carranza, Ivan Alejo has been yellow-carded for the home team.
